Sublime Actions

  Select Item – Ctrl+Shift+. or Ctrl+Shift+,

  Rename Tag – Ctrl+Shift+'
  Delete Tag – Ctrl+Shift+;

  Match Tag Pair Outward – Ctrl+,
  Match Tag Pair Inward – Ctrl+.

  Go to Matching Pair – Ctrl+Alt+J

  Go to Edit Point — Ctrl+Alt+→ or Ctrl+Alt+←

  Go to Anything — Ctrl+P

  Find — Ctrl+Shift+F

Navigation

  Focus Sidebar — ctrl+0
  Focus Group 0 — ctrl+1
  Focus Group 1 — ctrl+2
  Move to group 0 — ctrl+shift+1

  Ctrl + Alt + Up — Column selection up
  Ctrl + Alt + Down — Column selection up






empty spaces
^\n

trailing whitespace
[ \t]+\n
replace with
\n

-transition